Types.Doc: Declaration holds information about a go symbol.
Types.Name: Declaration

Fields.Name: Imports
Fields.Doc: This is not encoded to json, it's computed on load.

Types.Source:
// Declaration holds information about a go symbol.
type Declaration struct {
	Kind	DeclarationKind
	Type	string	`json:",omitempty"`

	File	string
	Line	int	`json:",omitempty"`

	SelfContained	bool

	// This is not encoded to json, it's computed on load.
	Imports	[]string	`json:"-"`

	References	StringSet	`json:",omitempty"`
	Globals		StringSet	`json:",omitempty"`

	Doc	string	`json:",omitempty"`

	Name		string		`json:",omitempty"`
	Names		[]string	`json:",omitempty"`
	Receiver	string		`json:",omitempty"`

	Fields	FieldList	`json:",omitempty"`

	Arguments	[]string	`json:",omitempty"`
	Returns		[]string	`json:",omitempty"`

	Signature	string	`json:",omitempty"`
	Source		string	`json:",omitempty"`

	Complexity	*Complexity	`json:",omitempty"`
}

Types.Doc: DeclarationKind is an enum of go symbol types.
Types.Name: DeclarationKind
Types.Source:
// DeclarationKind is an enum of go symbol types.
type DeclarationKind string

Types.Doc: DeclarationList holds a list of Go symbols.
Types.Name: DeclarationList
Types.Source:
// DeclarationList holds a list of Go symbols.
type DeclarationList []*Declaration

Types.Doc: Definition holds all symbols defined for a Package.
Types.Name: Definition
Types.Source:
// Definition holds all symbols defined for a Package.
type Definition struct {
	Package

	Doc	string	`json:",omitempty"`

	Imports		StringSet	`json:",omitempty"`
	InitCount	int		`json:",omitempty"`

	Types	DeclarationList	`json:",omitempty"`
	Consts	DeclarationList	`json:",omitempty"`
	Vars	DeclarationList	`json:",omitempty"`
	Funcs	DeclarationList	`json:",omitempty"`
}

Types.Doc: DefinitionList holds a list of Go packages.
Types.Name: DefinitionList
Types.Source:
// DefinitionList holds a list of Go packages.
type DefinitionList []*Definition

Types.Doc: Field holds details about a field definition.
Types.Name: Field

Fields.Name: Name
Fields.Doc: Name is the name of the field.

Fields.Name: Type
Fields.Doc: Type is the literal type of the Go field.

Fields.Name: Path
Fields.Doc: Path is the go path of this field starting from root object.

Fields.Name: Comment
Fields.Doc: Comment holds the field comment text.

Fields.Name: Tag
Fields.Doc: Tag is the go tag, unmodified.

Fields.Name: JSONName
Fields.Doc:
JSONName is the corresponding json name of the field.
It's cleared if it's set to `-` (unexported).

Fields.Name: MapKey
Fields.Doc: MapKey is the map key type, if this field is a map.

Types.Name: FieldList
Types.Source:
// FieldList contains all struct fields.
type FieldList []*Field

Types.Name: Package

Fields.Name: ID
Fields.Doc: ID is the ID of the package as x/tools packages loads it.

Fields.Name: Package
Fields.Doc: Package is the name of the package.

Fields.Name: Path
Fields.Doc: Path is sanitized to contain the relative location (folder).

Fields.Name: TestPackage
Fields.Doc: TestPackage is true if this is a test package.

Fields.Name: Complexity
Fields.Doc: Complexity to collect test coverage on package.

Fields.Name: Pkg
Fields.Doc:
Pkg serves to carry ast package information, preventing a double Load().
It's used during analysis and merging and discarded for the result.
